@startuml
!theme mars

title State Machine: Document Lifecycle

[*] --> Submitted : Client uploads image
Submitted --> S3Download : country inferred
S3Download --> RunOCR : download complete
RunOCR --> ParseFields : raw text extracted
ParseFields --> Validate : DocumentInfo populated

Validate --> PersistUser : PASSED
PersistUser --> EmitCompleted
EmitCompleted --> [*]

Validate --> PersistFailed : FAILED
S3Download --> PersistFailed : download error
Submitted --> PersistFailed : unknown country
ParseFields --> PersistFailed : parse error
RunOCR --> PersistFailed : OCR error

PersistFailed --> EmitFailed
EmitFailed --> [*]

state Submitted : S3 key parsed, country inferred
state S3Download : image downloaded to /tmp
state RunOCR : Tesseract extracts raw text
state ParseFields : country-specific field extraction
state Validate : checksum / format check
state PersistUser : PutUserIdentity to DynamoDB
state EmitCompleted : processing.completed event
state PersistFailed : PutFailedRecord to DynamoDB
state EmitFailed : processing.failed event

@enduml
